txt.en: Gothmog's scouts and defenders are patrolling the area and must be defeated.\n\nYou should defeat Orc scouts and defenders.
You thinned the ranks of Gothmog's forces in the area.\n\nYou should return to Dolenthol and inform him of your success.

'The forces arrayed against us will make it difficult for the Rangers to explore further into Minas Morgul. We must thin the ranks of Gothmog's scouts and defenders if we are to have success in this. Will you see it done?'
Gothmog's forces are scattered throughout the area. Dolenthol asked you to seek out and defeat both scouts and defenders.
'Without your assistance, our mission here would have been much more difficult. Here is a small token of our appreciation.'
